posting_body: ["DON'T MISS THIS OPPORTUNITY:", 'This Gorgeous POOL HOUSE has been just renovated and is ready for a new tenant to call it home!', 'Brand new kitchen offers white shaker cabinets, quartz countertops, glass tile backsplash, top of the line samsung appliances.', 'The Family Room and Living Room open to a convenient covered patio overlooking the beautiful pool with a jacuzzi and waterfall, perfect for entertainment!', 'All Bathrooms have been renovated with modern porcelain tiles, modern vanities and frameless glass shower doors.', 'Rent includes pool and yard maintenance.', 'The Gated Community of The Falls offers 24/7 guard at the gate, pool, playground, volleyball court and it is conveniently located on a wonderful school district, close to Publix, Starbuck & more!.', 'Easy to show on a lockbox.', 'RENTBROWARDHOMES.COM', 'Helping people find rentals since 2012!', 'TEXT FOR FASTEST RESPONSE:', 'show contact info', 'RENTBROWARDHOMES.COM', 'We specialize in Broward County Rentals.', 'I can text you a list of all the rentals available in the area.', 'Fast approval, NO HOA for some properties.', 'Pet friendly for some!', 'Proof of income is the most  important thing.', 'We can help people with bad credit or no credit!', "Let me know what you're looking for and I will find the right place regardless of the situation!", 'Brittini Flinn', 'SUN OCEAN REALTY', 'NO EMAIL', 'TEXT FOR FASTEST RESPONSE:', 'show contact info', 'RENTBROWARDHOMES.COM', 'PLEASE REFER TO TYN112437781']
